            <lg xml:id="TK539">
<l>ikaḻcciyiṟ keṭṭārai yeṇṇuka tānta</l>
<l> makiḻcciyiṉ maintuṟum pōḻtu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let (a king) think of those who have been ruined by neglect, when his mind is elated with joy.</l>
